    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💣 <i>Feathers. Firepower. Fowl play.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get ready to ruffle some feathers in <strong>War Pigeons</strong>, a chaotic, over-the-top <strong>platform fighter</strong> where militarized pigeons duke it out with everything from grenades to tanks! Take flight (literally) as you <strong>jump, flap, and blast</strong> your way through interactive arenas in this explosive party game.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🐦 <strong>Features</strong>:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💥 <strong>Birds with Guns</strong>: Equip your pigeons with a wild arsenal of weapons — pistols, tornados, grenades, tanks, super serums. Tactical? Maybe. Chaos? Definitely.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150210/extras/3098acace22fdee38c478f1c8e105615.poster.avif?t=1757761496\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150210/extras/3098acace22fdee38c478f1c8e105615.webm?t=1757761496\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150210/extras/3098acace22fdee38c478f1c8e105615.mp4?t=1757761496\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🕊️ <strong>Flight Meets Fight</strong>: Shoot, flap, and divebomb your enemies across vibrant 2.5D battlefields.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🎮 <strong>Online &amp; Local Multiplayer</strong>: Challenge your friends in chaotic 2–4 player matches.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🧠 <strong>Battle with Strategy (or just wing it)</strong>: Use terrain, timing, and sheer dumb luck to claim victory.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150210/extras/4671f870cee496b1d52a6a8623489524.poster.avif?t=1757761496\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150210/extras/4671f870cee496b1d52a6a8623489524.webm?t=1757761496\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150210/extras/4671f870cee496b1d52a6a8623489524.mp4?t=1757761496\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🌍 <strong>Wacky Warzones</strong>: Fight across rooftops, sewers, and top-secret bird bases, all fully armed and each map with its own hazards and interactable elements.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🐦<strong> Customization:</strong> Create the perfect pigeon to take to war! Choose your bird, your colors and a plethora of hats and accessories.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150210/extras/2d73114ba9a9f656ad9f2f7783ced790.poster.avif?t=1757761496\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150210/extras/2d73114ba9a9f656ad9f2f7783ced790.webm?t=1757761496\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150210/extras/2d73114ba9a9f656ad9f2f7783ced790.mp4?t=1757761496\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >🐣 <strong>Emotes Galore:</strong> Use emotes to interact with your friends or to show them who really at the top when you win. <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150210/extras/c221c7bca9a0a36cc9018e0395f0cfd0.poster.avif?t=1757761496\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150210/extras/c221c7bca9a0a36cc9018e0395f0cfd0.webm?t=1757761496\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3150210/extras/c221c7bca9a0a36cc9018e0395f0cfd0.mp4?t=1757761496\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >🦅 <strong>It's War Pigeons.</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether you’re pecking your way to the top or just here to cause pandemonium, <i>War Pigeons</i> brings high-flying, bomb-dropping, beak-smashing action like you’ve never seen before.</p>",
